thing illegal about the ball coming into contact with a player&rsquo;s arm or hand. It&rsquo;s only when the player deliberately creates that contact (or uses unintentional contact in a deliberate manner) in an attempt to control or manipulate the movement of the ball."},{"pid":"a1eaf4713eb2889b5db77ccc4cc2c74ed5e27681","tid":718493,"uid":4225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4f533ac88be98cf9ead1b20dafe930f288c6dd33","tid":718493,"uid":166434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"186d06fc0c8f6665dd94f91e46e458ca10c2df0b","tid":718493,"uid":158889,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T19:59:18.000Z","msg":"手球完得益既係對面 仲要起哂腳炒飛機 點比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:10:01.000Z","msg":"你on9<br />\n跟球例定跟你喜好呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:17:51.000Z","msg":"你on9<br />\n而家你定球證熟例呀？"},{"pid":"3bc92667a33822432dd9db886344bb68affaa8c9","tid":718493,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2c9d7d3a2add4181b3bb2c6448a7e7976524a8e","tid":718493,"uid":21152,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:08:48.000Z","msg":"幾時開始波打手要比十二碼？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:18:19.000Z","msg":"前一晚都係02:00am開波E朗對C朗無睇？"},{"pid":"68ce55a348fd0d34582a8772af7cbe1e2c48c725","tid":718493,"uid":166434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a1eaf4713eb2889b5db77ccc4cc2c74ed5e27681","tid":718493,"uid":4225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4f533ac88be98cf9ead1b20dafe930f288c6dd33","tid":718493,"uid":166434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"186d06fc0c8f6665dd94f91e46e458ca10c2df0b","tid":718493,"uid":158889,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T19:59:18.000Z","msg":"手球完得益既係對面 仲要起哂腳炒飛機 點比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:10:01.000Z","msg":"你on9<br />\n跟球例定跟你喜好呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:17:51.000Z","msg":"你on9<br />\n而家你定球證熟例呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:19:10.000Z","msg":"球證熟但黑呢<br />\non9"},{"pid":"1a089a1f0cd9fbcecb62ff9590976e9990f6f2ad","tid":718493,"uid":51936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:19:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得個球證好pro!<br />\n睇球員嘅意識係用頭頂，波打手無意手球<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32133ac6c83653d067fd15c7c1a2aebe4dc2721c","tid":718493,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba51f12653a9d961805b4ec0c0dd2e5c333cd8d7","tid":718493,"uid":56147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:17:01.000Z","msg":"fifia  講手球 就得4隻字 &quot;handles the ball deliberately&quot; (p.36)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fifa.com/mm/document/footballdevelopment/refereeing/81/42/36/log2013en_neutral.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fifa.com%2Fmm%2Fdocument%2Ffootballdevelopment%2Frefereeing%2F81%2F42%2F36%2Flog2013en_neutral.pdf&d=S0HjS%2BWY6eXWV7Mb2ORK2Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d892cb09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fifa.com/mm/document/footballdevelopment/refereeing/81/42/36/log2013en_neutral.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@Dobens/understanding-the-hand-ball-rule-1cc09a7a2239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40Dobens%2Funderstanding-the-hand-ball-rule-1cc09a7a2239&d=S0HjS%2BWY6eXWV7Mb2ORK2Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=8949ed54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@Dobens/understanding-the-hand-ball-rule-1cc09a7a2239</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAccording to FIFA&rsquo;s Laws of the Game, there is absolutely nothing illegal about the ball coming into contact with a player&rsquo;s arm or hand. It&rsquo;s only when the player deliberately creates that contact (or uses unintentional contact in a deliberate manner) in an attempt to control or manipulate the movement of the ball."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:20:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://football-technology.fifa.com/media/1245/lotg_17_18_en.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball-technology.fifa.com%2Fmedia%2F1245%2Flotg_17_18_en.pdf&d=S0HjS%2BWY6eXWV7Mb2ORK2Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=89d4c9ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://football-technology.fifa.com/media/1245/lotg_17_18_en.pdf</a><br />\n17-18年update版98頁啊傻<br />\n<br />\nHandling the ball<br />\n<br />\nHandling the ball involves a deliberate act of a player making contact with the<br />\nball with the hand or arm.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The following must be considered:<br />\n&bull;&ensp;the movement of the hand towards the ball (not the ball towards the hand)<br />\n&bull;&ensp;the distance between the opponent and the ball (unexpected ball)<br />\n&bull;&ensp;the position of the hand does not necessarily mean that there is an offence<br />\n&bull;&ensp;touching the ball with an object held in the hand (clothing, shinguard, etc.)<br />\nis an offence<br />\n&bull;&ensp;hitting the ball with a thrown object (boot, shinguard, etc.) is an offence</span><br />\n<br />\nThe goalkeeper has the same restrictions on handling the ball as any other<br />\nplayer outside the penalty area. Inside their penalty area, the goalkeeper<br />\ncannot be guilty of a handling offence incurring a direct free kick or any related<br />\nsanction but can be guilty of handling offences that incur an indirect free kick."},{"pid":"2946a42f318951023b3de969dfd164c6cec196c2","tid":718493,"uid":90081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:20:36.000Z","msg":"球證做嘢唔駛你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735017e69e40037f2d83a940cd125a6eb5cfe510","tid":718493,"uid":3331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17dd3e6a6c8ee8667d8efb8a7d27c4066b059cb","tid":718493,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T20:25:00.000Z","msg":"Var 方便莊家操控走地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}